# Input

```grit
`const capital = $val` where {
  $capitals = { england: `london`, ours: $val },
  $capitals.ours <: `paris`,
  $val => $capitals.england,
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
`const capital = $val` where {
	$capitals = { england: `london` , ours: $val },
	$capitals.ours <: `paris`,
	$val => $capitals.england
}

```
